description:
Juno Computers unveils the Neptune 17 v6 Linux-powered laptop with a 14th Gen Intel Core processor, up to NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4090 graphics, up to 64GB RAM, and up to 6TB SSD storage.

The post Juno Computers Launches Neptune 17 v6 Linux Laptop with Up to NVIDIA RTX 4090 appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Juno Computers Launches Neptune 17 v6 Linux Laptop with Up to NVIDIA RTX 4090
